## Celestial Bodies — OOP Project

C++ project demonstrating object-oriented programming concepts.

### Concepts used
- Abstract classes and pure virtual functions
- Multiple inheritance (CelestialBody + Planet + Explorer)
- Polymorphism and method overriding
- Dynamic memory allocation (new/delete)
- Class hierarchies (GasGiant → GasRingPlanet)

### Classes
- CelestialBody — base class with name and equator
- Planet — base class with distance, gravity, water
- Explorer — abstract interface with pure virtual explore()
- GasGiant — inherits all three
- RockyPlanet — inherits all three
- GasRingPlanet — extends GasGiant with ring data
